nt.  Expressed otherwise this issue is not merger specific.  SACTWU\'92s concerns about cheaper imports cannot be cured by the imposition of a merger condition on a single firm.  It is a sector- wide, phenomenon and must be addressed at that aggregated level 
with the appropriate instruments.     }
